name: labor_paramete_lod
action: <*ASSIGNVALUE(labor_parameter_lod:[IF](<*ISSELECTED(Level of Documentation.No Documentation)*>){0}{[IF](<*ISSELECTED(Level of Documentation.Screen Captures Only)*>){0.1}{0.25}[ENDIF]}[ENDIF])*>
description:
If lod = No Documentation, LD = 0
Else If lod = Screen Captures, LD = 0.1
Else LD = 0.25
